      "content": "but she says that just to be nice, you know? i know her. she's tired. i see her sighing when she comes in the room. it's like i'm a task she has to complete every day. if i could just find a way to go quietly, without a big fuss or any pain, wouldn't that be better for everyone? wouldn't it just be a relief for her to have her life back?",
